# Vercel should only see the static landing page assets under `web/`.
# Everything else in this repo (Swift sources, Xcode project, build artifacts,
# release scripts, GitHub Pages content, plans) is unrelated to the website.
#
# Vercel's Root Directory setting in the dashboard should be set to `web`,
# which already scopes the deploy. This file is belt-and-suspenders so that
# running `vercel` from the repo root (or any accidental scope change) does
# not try to upload the whole tree.

*
!web/
!web/**
